	<h2 class="modhead">Latest cycling Stories</h2>
	
<div class="topstories">

	<div class="topstory  clearfix">
		<div class="leadimage"><a href="/sports/cycling/story/2012/08/30/sp-cycling-tyler-hamilton-lance-armstrong-tour-de-france-performance-enhancing-drugs.html"><img src="/gfx/images/sports/photos/2012/08/30/hamilton-tyler_940-default.jpg" alt="Tyler Hamilton says Lance Armstrong gave him illegal drug" border="0" /></a></div>
