			<dt class="headline"><a href="/sports/cycling/story/2012/08/30/sp-cycling-tyler-hamilton-lance-armstrong-tour-de-france-performance-enhancing-drugs.html">Tyler Hamilton says Lance Armstrong gave him illegal drug</a> <span class="socialicons" title="2000528955"></span>
